data.description: Amazing 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home with side entry 2 car garage plus detached 2 car garage! Huge rocking chair front porch with screened door that leads guest to the foyer with crown molding! Open floor plan with high ceilings, beautiful LVP flooring & upgraded lighting! Living room with vaulted ceiling, fan & fireplace! Kitchen with large island/breakfast bar, pantry, gas range plus 2nd wall oven, built in microwave, dishwasher, tiled backsplash, granite countertops & breakfast room with wainscoting! Dining room with crown molding & wainscoting! Fantastic sunroom with tray ceiling & wet bar with granite countertop, tiled backsplash & open shelving! Split floor plan! Owner suite with walk-in closet, tray ceiling, fan & enough room for sitting area!  Owners bathroom with double sink vanity with middle cabinet for added storage, framed mirrors, tiled shower, soaking tub & water closet! Spacious spare bedrooms! Hall bathroom with double sink vanity & tiled floor! Mudbench from the garage! Half bath for guests! Laundry room! Covered porch with extended deck overlooking privacy fenced backyard with firepit, built in seating at the wood line & walkway to custom gate at walking trail which is just beyond the property line! Added patio under deck with cozy nooks, great for relaxing! Great storage room in walk in crawl space! Added gutters, nice curb appeal, landscape lights & added palm trees! This home is a must see with so much to offer whether entertaining or enjoying everyday life all in wonderful Retreat at Storm Branch neighborhood with resort style swimming pool & walking trails!
